{"tid":702041,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余香凝認有去Victor屋企過夜","createTime":"2018-06-14T14:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T17:22:53.000Z","uid":180713,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3820d5941e5c03f526fcf6aa4254d7f9ba3dcdbe","tid":702041,"uid":180713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"余香凝接受訪問時表示與陳家樂分手絕對不涉第三者，但有指她在Victor家過夜？她指Victor是認識很耐的朋友，她說：「最近我哋夾分搞一間食肆，仲有其他生意夥伴，每一次開會都唔係淨係得我哋兩個，加上我將要離港一個月，而間舖月底就開張，有好多事要傾，所以每日做完工作，即使幾夜我都會上Victor屋企開會，<span style=\"color: green;\"> 上面係有佢屋企人，有其他生意夥伴，所以絕對唔係淨係得我哋兩個。</span>」 <br />\n<br />\n她續說：「呢件事一路係好秘密緊進行，畢竟係一個投資，有好多嘢處理，每一晚都要開會研究一啲嘢食。（真係有過夜？）係，有試過開通宵。（你同佢係咪拍拖？）絕對唔係，佢係朋友同生意夥伴。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180614/mobile/bkn-20180614154622277-0614_00862_001.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180614%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180614154622277-0614_00862_001.html%20&d=0Y3mLRbNltT6Qu%2BdO6JA6P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7e4fbc75\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180614/mobile/bkn-20180614154622277-0614_00862_001.html </a><br />\n<br />\n送到上門都仲死撐<br />\n又會淨係影到你出入嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心痛家樂BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f441e2512898e34c1578556b8000ac55b165d5a7","tid":702041,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"臭G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38f188d2253d8da89d7a81e6b9b306d5c188987","tid":702041,"uid":180713,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"f441e2512898e34c1578556b8000ac55b165d5a7","tid":702041,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"臭G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T14:38:31.000Z","